Description: A data.table-based toolkit for constructing firm-year panels from
    licensed Bureau van Dijk Orbis and Amadeus exports, resolving account-type
    duplication, handling historical vintages, adding ownership indicators,
    benchmarking against Eurostat Structural Business Statistics and Business
    Demography via the CRAN package eurodata, and computing SME and industry
    concentration diagnostics. The package translates the approach and replication
    code of Kalemli-Özcan, Sørensen, Villegas-Sanchez, Volosovych, and Yeşiltaş
    (2024) <doi:10.1257/mac.20220036> into reusable R functions. It does not
    redistribute Orbis data.
